1) enable remote ssh from raspi-config
2) give static ip of 10.42.0.15, gateway 10.42.0.1 dnserver 8.8.8.8 8.8.4.4 from edit connections 
3) in your device edit eth connection to shared to other devices
4) disable GUI
5) install git sudo apt install git
6) clone PI repo and run install_ros.sh
7) remove cloned PI :-) it was just to run install_ros.sh
8) sudo i2cdetect -y 1



Networking ...
	to get ip address over wifi use sudo nmap -sP 192.168.1.*
	


